---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="홈">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1 class="sudo-remove">SUDO REMOVE</h1>
    <p class="tagline">AI의 문턱을 낮추다</p>
    <p class="sub-tagline">함께 만들고, 바로 따라할 수 있는 AI 프로젝트</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/community/docs/physical-ai/lerobot/tutorials" class="btn btn-primary">바로 시작하기</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/orgs/sudormrf-run/discussions" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">커뮤니티 참여</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>우리가 하는 일</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>커뮤니티</h3>
        <p>함께 만들고 공유하는 AI 프로젝트 커뮤니티를 운영합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>오픈소스</h3>
        <p>모든 프로젝트와 코드를 공개하여 바로 따라할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>컨설팅</h3>
        <p>AI 기술 도입과 활용을 위한 맞춤형 컨설팅을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="youtube-section">
    <h2>YouTube 콘텐츠</h2>
    <div class="youtube-grid">
      <div class="youtube-card">
        <h3>팟캐스트</h3>
        <div class="youtube-embed">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLLYXs4EFjbmlC86qaN9FXSK7ib0y3h3jN" 
            title="SUDO REMOVE 팟캐스트"
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="youtube-card">
        <h3>미니 다큐</h3>
        <div class="youtube-embed">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HgN0qIFSd8I" 
            title="SUDO REMOVE 미니 다큐"
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="current-focus">
    <h2>On Going Projects</h2>
    <div class="focus-content">
      <h3>HuggingFace LeRobot으로 만드는 Physical AI</h3>
      <p>로봇 팔을 직접 조립하고, AI로 제어하는 실전 프로젝트를 함께 만들어갑니다.</p>
      <a href="/community/docs/physical-ai/lerobot/intro" class="btn btn-primary">바로 시작하기</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* 배경색 강제 적용 */
  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }
  
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #0d030f;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-orange), var(--color-yellow), var(--color-green));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.5));
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-orange);
    color: var(--color-bg-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-red);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-green);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-green);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-bg-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.4);
  }

  /* YouTube 섹션 */
  .youtube-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .youtube-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .youtube-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .youtube-card {
    background: rgba(13, 3, 15, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  
  .youtube-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-orange);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.2);
  }
  
  .youtube-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .youtube-embed {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 */
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 100%;
    background: #000;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .youtube-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .features {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .features h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(13, 3, 15, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.2);
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-orange), var(--color-yellow));
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-orange);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.2);
  }
  
  .feature-card:hover::before {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .current-focus {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.1), rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.1));
    border: 1px solid rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.3);
    padding: 1rem 3rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .current-focus::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .current-focus h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }

  .focus-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .focus-content p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
